<title>USA: Beachport Entertainment hires adviser.</title>
<headline>Beachport Entertainment hires adviser.</headline>
<dateline>LOS ANGELES 1997-04-22</dateline>
<text>
<p>Beachport Entertainment Corp said on Tuesday it agreed to engage New York-based BlueStone Capital Partners LP to act as Beachport's exclusive financial adviser.</p>
<p>BlueStone would assist and advise the company on various matters concerning corporate finance, mergers and acquisitions and capital formation, Beachport said.</p>
<p>Beachport Entertainment develops, produces and distributes an array of live family entertainment, sporting events and television programming.</p>
<p>((New York newsdesk 212-859-1610))</p>
